&gt; 
&gt; A few events I see that people here might be interested in:
&gt; 
&gt; Sat 7:00 PM
&gt; Independent Paranormal  Devil&#39;s Advocate  It seems paranormal research is believing in it&#39;s own ghosts.  These ghosts are called &quot;theories&quot;.  We will discuss several of the most popular &quot;theories&quot; that haunt us today.  Will you believe?
&gt; 
&gt; Sat 9:00 PM
&gt; Ghosts of Colorado  Join Rocky Mountain Paranormal Research Society as they bring you many of Colorado&#39;s best ghost stories, including some of their own.  Stayed tuned following the discussion for a showing of one of their favorite films.
&gt; 
&gt; Sun 9:00 AM
&gt; Are Aliens Invading Denver? (coffee and donut panel)  Are aliens invading Denver?  The real MIB exposed.  Join Baxter and Bryan in a closer look at claims of aliens living among us and the plans to form a welcoming committee for them.
&gt; 
&gt; Sun 2:00 PM
&gt; Evidence of the Paranormal? - Rocky Mountain Paranormal examines what is considered proof of the paranormal and whether or not it is actually proof.  Come join the discussion.
